00,000 international students each year to a variety of programs, ranging from English Language courses to PhDs. UK universities welcome students from many cultures and offer many services to help foreign students adapt to living and studying in the UK, including orientation activities, student advisors, language support, academic associations, social clubs and other programs. Living in the UK to study offer students a great multi-cultural experience both within the university and the community. It is a country with many attractions and experiences for visitors.<br \\/><br \\/>We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual UK graduates, many of whom have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements. We are also a registered UCAS (Universities and College Admissions Service) centre.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4ac6531\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"10886c8\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"16badc9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1cfc2a5b\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"border_border\":\"dotted\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"border_color\":\"#cccccc\",\"border_radius\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c6fd93\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3044ea57\",\"elType\":\"widget