nging, fun, and rewarding. As an international student in Australia, you can expect to live, grow and learn in a young, friendly country full of opportunities. For those international students who successfully complete their degree, they will soon find that they are competitive in today\\u2019s international job market. The Australian university campuses are safe and friendly with great facilities.<br \\/><br \\/>We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"b73922f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"83b5a3e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2e79863\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"5d125ea1\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"border_border\":\"dotted\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"border_color\":\"#cccccc\",\"border_radius\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6df6988d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5fd8f15c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/gmc\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/02\\/newzealand-flag.jpg\",\"id\":300},\"image_size\":\"custom\",\"image_custom_dimension\":{\"width\":\"144\",\"height\":\"72\"},\"align\":\"right\"},