	(14,1,'2019-01-28 11:22:45','2019-01-28 11:22:45','<h2>About Us</h2>\nGMC Studies is a British Council accredited student consultancy company. We offer counseling services to international students who intend to undertake higher education at institutions in the UK, USA, Australia, New Zealand, Canada, Malaysia, Russia, Ukraine, and Georgia. Our experienced counselors possess in-depth knowledge regarding higher education institutions, which enables them to assist our client-students in choosing the right programme at the right institution. Our expert advice is particularly beneficial for students from Middle-Eastern countries, as our counselors are fully aware of the education system and are capable of comprehending the attributes our client-students look for while choosing their destination for higher education.\n\n<img width=\"400\" height=\"299\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/about-us.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/about-us.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/about-us-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\">','About us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2019-01-29 15:19:42','2019-01-29 15:19:42','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=14',0,'page','',0),
