	(16,1,'2019-01-28 11:22:45','2019-01-28 11:22:45','<h2>Counseling</h2>\nAt GMC Studies, our emphasise is on providing our client-students with intensive education counseling, which ensures the smooth exchange of crucial information and assists in choosing the right course and institution. Our counselors have many years of experience in providing education and career counseling to students from Saudi Arabia, Kuwait, Qatar, Egypt, Oman, UAE, Iraq, Iran, Libya, and Jordan.\n\n<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/counsel.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/counsel.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/counsel-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\">','Counseling','','publish','closed','closed','','counseling','','','2019-02-05 04:42:56','2019-02-05 04:42:56','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=16',0,'page','',0),
	(17,1,'2019-01-28 11:22:45','2019-01-28 11:22:45','<h2>Application Processing</h2>		\n		<p>GMC Studies offers full support in processing applications to respected institutions. Our counselors painstakingly check the applications and attempt to process them expeditiously to ensure that our client-students get the most efficient service with extreme reliability.</p>		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/application-process.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/application-process.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/application-process-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','Application Processing','','publish','closed','closed','','application-processing','','','2019-02-05 05:50:29','2019-02-05 05:50:29','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=17',0,'page','',0),
