	(29,1,'2019-01-28 11:23:27','2019-01-28 11:23:27','<figure><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/slide1-1-1024x260.jpg\" alt=\"slide1\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/slide2-1024x260.jpg\" alt=\"slide2\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/slide3-1024x260.jpg\" alt=\"slide3\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/slide4-1024x260.jpg\" alt=\"slide4\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/slide5-1024x260.jpg\" alt=\"slide5\" /></figure>			\n			<h3>Welcome To GMC Studies</h3>		\n		<p>Studies GMC is a British Council accredited student consultancy company. We offer counseling services to international students intend to Undertake WHO at higher education institutions in the UK, USA, Australia, New Zealand, Canada, Malaysia, Russia, Ukraine, and Georgia.</p><p>Our experienced counselors POSSESS in-depth knowledge Regarding Higher Education Institutions, Which Enables them to assist our client-students in choosing the right Program at the right institution. Our expert advice is Particularly beneficial for Students from Middle-Eastern Countries.</p>		\n										<img width=\"711\" height=\"432\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/wel-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/wel-img.jpg 711w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/wel-img-300x182.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 711px) 100vw, 711px\" />											\n			<figure><img width=\"182\" height=\"176\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ball-coun.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3><h1 style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 36px; font-family: &quot;Ope