	(232,1,'2019-02-12 16:43:09','2019-02-12 16:43:09','<h2>Accommodation</h2>		\n		<p>We understand the individual needs of our client-students and we endeavour to ensure that you secure an appropriate place to live before arriving at your chosen institution. We work with the accommodation departments of various educational institutions along with private accommodation providers.</p>		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accomodation.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accomodation.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accomodation-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','Accommodation','','publish','closed','closed','','accommodation','','','2019-02-12 16:48:59','2019-02-12 16:48:59','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=232',0,'page','',0),
	(233,1,'2019-02-12 16:43:09','2019-02-12 16:43:09','<h2>English Language Programmes</h2>		\n		Learning the English language can be regarded as the first step towards higher education in the West. There is a wide range of programmes being offered by renowned institutions. General English language courses are for beginners or those who have only basic English language skills. There are specifically designed academic courses for international students being offered by both English language schools and higher education institutions. There are also Pre-Sessional English language programmes which are integrated with your academic programme.\nWe can assist you to find the right type of English language programme. Our Counsellors are highly trained in assessing your English language skills and placing you in a suitable course. We carefully plan a progression path for our Client-Students with specific attention to their desired outcome from their higher education. We work closely with a large number of English language institutes and can assist you in securing a place in the UK, USA, Australia, New Zealand, Canada, Malaysia.		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/English-Language-Programmes.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/English-Language-Programmes.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/English-Language-Programmes-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','English Language Programmes','','publish','closed','closed','','english-language-programmes','','','2019-02-12 16:52:55','2019-02-12 16:52:55','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=233',0,'page','',0),
	(234,1,'2019-02-12 16:43:09','2019-02-12 16:43:09','<h2>Undergraduate Studies</h2>		\n		A large number of international students travel overseas for pursuing undergraduate studies. International students often have to undertake pathway or foundational programmes in order to progress to the undergraduate studies of their choice. Foundation courses are offered by a number of providers. There are several intakes for foundation programmes and the English language requirement may vary accordingly. The application process for undergraduate courses is highly competitive.\nOur Counsellors have in-depth knowledge about the admission requirements and course structure. We have partnerships with all major pathway providers and we work closely with universities in the UK, USA, Australia, New Zealand, Canada, Malaysia, Russia, Ukraine and Georgia for placing international students at undergraduate level programmes. We can guide you through all the necessary steps including application submission, visa guidance, and accommodation arrangement.		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Undergraduate-Studies.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Undergraduate-Studies.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Undergraduate-Studies-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','Undergraduate Studies','','publish','closed','closed','','undergraduate-studies','','','2019-02-12 16:59:57','2019-02-12 16:59:57','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=234',0,'page','',0),
	(235,1,'2019-02-12 16:43:09','2019-02-12 16:43:09','<h2>Postgraduate Taught Programmes</h2>		\n		Most taught postgraduate courses last for one year and lead to a Master’s (MA, MSc) Degree. The programmes consist of coursework, examinations, and dissertation or final project. Taught postgraduate courses are popular among international students. Most of the universities offer these courses in a wide range of subject areas.\nWe can assist you in finding an appropriate postgraduate course. Our Counsellors are familiar with a wide range of courses and are capable of guiding you through the application process. We can also assist you in meeting the English language requirements by arranging a place on an appropriate English language course.		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Postgraduate-Taught-Programmes.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Postgraduate-Taught-Programmes.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Postgraduate-Taught-Programmes-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','Postgraduate Taught Programmes','','publish','closed','closed','','postgraduate-taught-programmes','','','2019-02-12 17:08:01','2019-02-12 17:08:01','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=235',0,'page','',0),
	(236,1,'2019-02-12 16:43:09','2019-02-12 16:43:09','<h2>Postgraduate Research Programmes</h2>		\n		Most UK universities undertake research and teaching, although the mission focus and balance of activities vary. Some institutions concentrate primarily on teaching while others are more research intensive. Universities also increasingly transfer knowledge out to businesses and other organisations. Universities also seek to use their expertise and facilities to develop thriving social and business communities in their region.\nWe can guide you through the process of becoming a research student at UK universities. The application process differs when it comes to MPhil or Ph.D. programmes. Our Counsellors are experienced in assisting research applicants. You will be assigned to our dedicated team, who will explain the entire process methodically and provide you with necessary information and guidance.		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Postgraduate-Research-Programmes.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Postgraduate-Research-Programmes.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Postgraduate-Research-Programmes-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','Postgraduate Research Programmes','','publish','closed','closed','','postgraduate-research-programmes','','','2019-02-12 17:09:23','2019-02-12 17:09:23','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=236',0,'page','',0),
