	(238,1,'2019-02-12 16:43:10','2019-02-12 16:43:10','<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/uk-flag-o3f41arn5e8m5wg8hhkjhaijk59h4kxcq5iqjlgjbk.jpg\" title=\"uk-flag\" alt=\"uk-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in UK</h3>		\n		<p>The UK is a world leader in many areas of education including engineering, science, art and design, business and management, law and finance. The UK’s reputation and legacy as a world centre for scientific research makes it a magnet for some of the very best thinkers in the world. With only one per cent of the world’s population, the UK is responsible for eight per cent of global scientific publications. The UK offers a world-renowned education system with qualifications that can make a real difference to your future. It attracts over 600,000 international students each year to a variety of programs, ranging from English Language courses to PhDs. UK universities welcome students from many cultures and offer many services to help foreign students adapt to living and studying in the UK, including orientation activities, student advisors, language support, academic associations, social clubs and other programs. Living in the UK to study offer students a great multi-cultural experience both within the university and the community. It is a country with many attractions and experiences for visitors.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual UK graduates, many of whom have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements. We are also a registered UCAS (Universities and College Admissions Service) centre.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/us-flag-o3f419tsyk7buahlmz5wwsr2yre3wvtme0v92bhxhs.jpg\" title=\"us-flag\" alt=\"us-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in US</h3>		\n		<p>The US is home to the highest number of international students in the world. With famous cities, epic landscapes, highly ranked universities and exciting campus environments, studying in the US offers the perfect blend of educational quality and cultural experience.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/ireland-flag-o3f4jzs32rtx2panbkhf2kokw14a7v55yome5pqnkg.jpg\" title=\"ireland-flag\" alt=\"ireland-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Ireland</h3>		\n		<p>Ireland is one of the most sought after foreign education destinations in the world. Known for its beautiful landscapes and mountains, it is a lovely place for you to study. It is the second largest island of The British Isles and is a land of mesmerizing green beauty. It is called Eire that is named after the Goddess of the land and is an ancient Gaelic term. The advantage of study in Ireland is that you will find a well-structured education system here as well as top universities and outstanding post- study career options.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/canada-flag-o3f4jyu8vxsmr3c0h22si2x4an8x061fmjywofs1qo.jpg\" title=\"canada-flag\" alt=\"canada-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Canada</h3>		\n		<p>Increasingly, students around the world are discovering the advantages of going to universities in Canada. The attractions for studying in Canada are: first-rate education, diverse study opportunities, safe and friendly communities. In 2015-16, there were more than 144,500 full-time and 24,100 part-time international students from more than 200 countries went to Canadian institutes. Canadian degrees are highly regarded all over the globe, and international students choose Canada for higher education that will lead to successful careers.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/china-flag-o3f4jyu8vxsmr3c0h22si2x4an8x061fmjywofs1qo.jpg\" title=\"china-flag\" alt=\"china-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in China</h3>		\n		<p>Further education in China has been on an upward trend for the past decades. Further studies in China are fast catching up as the world’s 3rd hottest study destination right behind U.S. and UK which remains as the 1st and 2nd position respectively among international students worldwide. According to the latest statistics released by the China Ministry of Education, the number of international students studying in China continues to climb, reaching 442,773 in 2016, the students came from over 200 countries and regions studying in China and putting it on track to reach its target of hosting half a million international students by 2020.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/australia-flag-o3f4jxwep3rcfhddmjo5xl5np9djsgxpafbf75tfww.jpg\" title=\"australia-flag\" alt=\"australia-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Australia</h3>		\n		<p>Australia promotes innovation, creativity and independent thinking throughout its universities. International students who study and live in Australia soon find that their education is challenging, fun, and rewarding. As an international student in Australia, you can expect to live, grow and learn in a young, friendly country full of opportunities. For those international students who successfully complete their degree, they will soon find that they are competitive in today’s international job market. The Australian university campuses are safe and friendly with great facilities.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/newzealand-flag-o3f4rupi7wl85bvofgs4f3abp0drkrcddkzjm035jk.jpg\" title=\"newzealand-flag\" alt=\"newzealand-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in New Zealand</h3>		\n		<p>New Zealand offers a world-class education in a postcard-perfect environment. New Zealand has an excellent, centrally managed quality assurance system. The New Zealand Qualifications Authority (NZQA) requires that institutions are registered to enroll international students and ensures compliance with qualifications standards. Seven New Zealand universities were ranked in the top 400 universities in the world for 2018 by the Times Higher Education World University Rankings. New Zealand has always been internationally recognized for its excellent education standards and for training high quality teachers, which makes it a given fact that the institutions in New Zealand provide one of the best world class teaching faculties. Apart from this, New Zealand also has a high quality of amenities and research facilities for its students.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/malaysia-flag-o3f4rtro12jxtpx1kydhuliv3mied28n1gc24q4jps.jpg\" title=\"malaysia-flag\" alt=\"malaysia-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Malaysia</h3>		\n		<p>The graduate education system in Malaysia is the same as many other countries, such as the UK but there is a higher number of private universities in Malaysia. There is a wide choice of graduate programs including Masters degrees and research PHD studies at Malaysian universities, and foreign university branch campuses in the country. Postgraduate study in Malaysia offers high quality teaching with a relatively affordable cost of education and easy immigration procedures compared to other countries.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/russia-flag-o3f4rsttu8ini3yeqfyva3rei8n15d4wpbokng5xw0.jpg\" title=\"russia-flag\" alt=\"russia-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Russia</h3>		\n		<p>There are 24 universities in Russia featured within the QS World University Rankings® 2018, 10 of which are placed among the top 400 universities worldwide. Russia also boasts a substantial presence in the QS EECA University Rankings, a ranking of the 300 leading universities in emerging Europe and central Asia, with a whopping 95 Russian universities currently featured. Over the past decade or so, higher education in Russia has undergone significant change, with 390 billion rubles (~US$6.7 billion) allocated between 2011 and 2015 for upgrading facilities and technical equipment at Russian universities and improving training for teaching staff. Additionally, in 2003, Russia signed up to the Bologna Process, pledging to bring its system in line with most other countries across Europe. This means many universities in Russia now offer a choice between a four-year bachelor’s degree and a five-year specialist degree. Russia’s higher education system was ranked 15th in the world, in the 2018 edition of the QS Higher Education System Strength Rankings. We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/ukraine-flag-o3f4rsttu8ini3yeqfyva3rei8n15d4wpbokng5xw0.jpg\" title=\"ukraine-flag\" alt=\"ukraine-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Ukraine</h3>		\n		<p>Ukraine University World ranking is averagely high. Many of their Universities are of high standard with big structures and very qualified teachers. Please make sure you do your proper research about the University of your Choice before you even apply. We can help you with that information for free if you contact us.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/georgia-flag-o3f4rrvznehd6hzrvxk8plzxwurnxo16d713667c28.jpg\" title=\"georgia-flag\" alt=\"georgia-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Georgia</h3>		\n		<p>International students are welcomed into Georgia and will find world class universities with a high standard and quality of education. The courses are taught in English, however students do not need a TOFEL or IELTS test result to be accepted, students simply need to be read and understand English. Georgia universities have low tuition fees and living costs. They provide good university accommodation and a high European standard of living, including a first-rate transport system. We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>','Study Destinations','','publish','closed','closed','','study-destinations','','','2019-02-13 04:13:54','2019-02-13 04:13:54','',0,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/?page_id=238',0,'page','',0),
