	(271,1,'2019-02-12 16:47:43','2019-02-12 16:47:43','<h2>Visa Support</h2>		\n		<p>It is of crucial importance to ensure that you have successfully completed the immigration procedures. Meeting the immigration requirements on time will ensure you are able to join your chosen educational institution. At GMC Studies, our counselors and compliance team are committed to ensuring that you have a smooth journey towards your academic success by assisting you in understanding immigration rules and submitting visa applications</p>		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/visa-support.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/visa-support.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/visa-support-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','Visa Support','','inherit','closed','closed','','230-revision-v1','','','2019-02-12 16:47:43','2019-02-12 16:47:43','',230,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/2019/02/12/230-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(272,1,'2019-02-12 16:48:59','2019-02-12 16:48:59','<h2>Accommodation</h2>		\n		<p>We understand the individual needs of our client-students and we endeavour to ensure that you secure an appropriate place to live before arriving at your chosen institution. We work with the accommodation departments of various educational institutions along with private accommodation providers.</p>		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accomodation.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accomodation.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accomodation-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','Accommodation','','inherit','closed','closed','','232-revision-v1','','','2019-02-12 16:48:59','2019-02-12 16:48:59','',232,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/2019/02/12/232-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(273,1,'2019-02-12 16:51:22','2019-02-12 16:51:22','<h2>English Language Programmes</h2>		\n		Learning the English language can be regarded as the first step towards higher education in the West. There is a wide range of programmes being offered by renowned institutions. General English language courses are for beginners or those who have only basic English language skills. There are specifically designed academic courses for international students being offered by both English language schools and higher education institutions. There are also Pre-Sessional English language programmes which are integrated with your academic programme.\nWe can assist you to find the right type of English language programme. Our Counsellors are highly trained in assessing your English language skills and placing you in a suitable course. We carefully plan a progression path for our Client-Students with specific attention to their desired outcome from their higher education. We work closely with a large number of English language institutes and can assist you in securing a place in the UK, USA, Australia, New Zealand, Canada, Malaysia.		\n										<img width=\"400\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/application-process.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/application-process.jpg 400w, http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/application-process-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" />','English Language Programmes','','inherit','closed','closed','','233-revision-v1','','','2019-02-12 16:51:22','2019-02-12 16:51:22','',233,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/2019/02/12/233-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
