	(294,1,'2019-02-12 17:25:44','2019-02-12 17:25:44','','ireland-flag','','inherit','open','closed','','ireland-flag','','','2019-02-12 17:25:44','2019-02-12 17:25:44','',238,'http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/ireland-flag.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),
	(295,1,'2019-02-12 17:29:13','2019-02-12 17:29:13','<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/uk-flag-o3f41arn5e8m5wg8hhkjhaijk59h4kxcq5iqjlgjbk.jpg\" title=\"uk-flag\" alt=\"uk-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in UK</h3>		\n		<p>The UK is a world leader in many areas of education including engineering, science, art and design, business and management, law and finance. The UK’s reputation and legacy as a world centre for scientific research makes it a magnet for some of the very best thinkers in the world. With only one per cent of the world’s population, the UK is responsible for eight per cent of global scientific publications. The UK offers a world-renowned education system with qualifications that can make a real difference to your future. It attracts over 600,000 international students each year to a variety of programs, ranging from English Language courses to PhDs. UK universities welcome students from many cultures and offer many services to help foreign students adapt to living and studying in the UK, including orientation activities, student advisors, language support, academic associations, social clubs and other programs. Living in the UK to study offer students a great multi-cultural experience both within the university and the community. It is a country with many attractions and experiences for visitors.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual UK graduates, many of whom have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements. We are also a registered UCAS (Universities and College Admissions Service) centre.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/us-flag-o3f419tsyk7buahlmz5wwsr2yre3wvtme0v92bhxhs.jpg\" title=\"us-flag\" alt=\"us-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in US</h3>		\n		<p>The US is home to the highest number of international students in the world. With famous cities, epic landscapes, highly ranked universities and exciting campus environments, studying in the US offers the perfect blend of educational quality and cultural experience.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/ireland-flag-o3f4jzs32rtx2panbkhf2kokw14a7v55yome5pqnkg.jpg\" title=\"ireland-flag\" alt=\"ireland-flag\" />											\n			<h3><br>Study in Ireland</h3>		\n		<p>Ireland is one of the most sought after foreign education destinations in the world. Known for its beautiful landscapes and mountains, it is a lovely place for you to study. It is the second largest island of The British Isles and is a land of mesmerizing green beauty. It is called Eire that is named after the Goddess of the land and is an ancient Gaelic term. The advantage of study in Ireland is that you will find a well-structured education system here as well as top universities and outstanding post- study career options.<br /><br />We understand that you expect to study at the best possible institution and our consultants are all multi-lingual graduates, many of who have undergone industry recognized and accredited training. You can be assured that GMC Consultants use the best possible information and their expertise to get you offers for the most appropriate course and university, which meets your requirements.</p>		\n										<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/gmc/